 right-hand man Scorpion, who find themselves embroiled in their father Ko's turf war against rival gangs in Taipei, setting off a conflict between old and new generations of gangsters. The film is the latest installment in the Gatao franchise, following the narrative of a young successor trying to expand his power while navigating the volatile underworld."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"角頭－鬥陣欸","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"發生在大橋頭事件之後，隨著 Michael 的離開，台灣角頭勢力陷入真空期，北部角頭版圖開始動搖，南部勢力蠢蠢欲動，故事圍繞著南北部六大巨頭（高捷、蔡振南、太保、喜翔、龍天翔、崔浩然）之間的爾虞我詐和南北角頭的勢力爭奪展開⋯⋯"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Gatao: Tal Pai, Tal Filho","runtime":131,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em Dingzhuang, uma cidade dominada por diversas gangues criminosas, dois irmãos, envolvidos em uma guerra do tráfico,  tentam sobreviver após se tornarem velhos conhecidos pelos poderosos traficantes do local. A trama, antes de tudo, mostra o impacto direto das ações dos criminosos no cotidiano de toda uma comunidade."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"角头：斗阵欸","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事发生在大桥头事件之后，随著Michael的离开，台湾角头势力陷入真空期，北部角头版图开始动摇，南部势力蠢蠢欲动，故事围绕著南北部六大巨头（高捷、蔡振南、太保、喜翔、龙天翔、崔浩然）之间的尔虞我诈和南北角头的势力争夺展开......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Đầu Đảng Giang Hồ: Kề Vai Chiến Đấu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Khi bố anh khơi mào cuộc chiến địa bàn dữ dội giữa các băng đảng đối thủ cả cũ lẫn mới, người đàn ông nọ cố gắng thâu tóm thế giới tội phạm ngầm đẫm máu của Đài Loan."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"가타오: 암흑가의 형제들","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"아버지가 촉발한 구세력과 신세력 사이의 치열한 영역 다툼. 이제 그 아들이 참전해 피로 물든 대만 범죄 세계 장악에 나선다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"เจ้าพ่อ: ศึกพี่ใหญ่","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เมื่อผู้เป็นพ่อจุดชนวนสงครามชิงเขตอิทธิพลระหว่างแก๊งอริทั้งเก่าและใหม่ ชายคนหนึ่งต้องหาทางยึดครองโลกใต้ดินอันนองเลือดในไต้หวัน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un homme tente de prendre le contrôle du monde criminel sanglant de Taïwan après que son père a déclenché une dangereuse guerre territoriale entre d'anciens et de nouveaux gangs rivaux."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Gatao Big Brothers","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un hombre intenta apoderarse del sangriento mundo criminal de Taiwán cuando su padre desata una explosiva guerra territorial entre bandas rivales antiguas y nuevas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Gatao: Big Brothers","runtime":123,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Lorsque son père déclenche une sanglante guerre de territoire entre d'anciens et de nouveaux gangs rivaux, un homme tente de prendre le contrôle de l'impitoyable pègre taiwanaise."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":77982,"adult":false,"title":"Wizards of Waverly Place: Wizard School","video":true,"overview":"When Alex is caught using magic to clean her room she is forced to go to wizard school with Justin. Max and Jerry camp out on the terrace to prove their manhood.","genre_ids":[10751,35,14,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7965,"vote_count":245,"poster_path":"/bdc2L2xnH55chbam8bOvxuSDYst.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-06","vote_average":8.955,"backdrop_path":"/j3jPLQ7HVSFoO32MPUPI2Xe04Vx.jpg","original_title":"Wizards of Waverly Place: Wizard School","original_language":"en"},{"id":366384,"adult":false,"title":"Hanna-Barbera's 50th","video":false,"overview":"The special is hosted by Tony Danza and Annie Potts celebrating 50 years of William Hanna and Joseph Barbera's partnership in animation. This is the first animated project to be broadcast in Dolby Surround sound system.","genre_ids":[35,14,10751,16,99,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3771,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/zusIo9ohmVsopbLfAnd4lQgU53P.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-17","vote_average":9.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hanna-Barbera's 50th","original_language":"en"},{"id":79078,"adult":false,"title":"11/11/11","video":false,"overview":"Jack and Melissa are frightened by their son's bizarre and violent behavior; they soon learn that he is the gateway to the Apocalypse, and it will happen on his birthday, 11-11-11.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3051,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/izah4Cw84whnwhwHqN7aJ1Kc2mR.jpg","release_date":"2011-11-01","vote_average":3.754,"backdrop_path":"/rsOoVOlS6qy68gTM2bIOp6fb8wA.jpg","original_title":"11/11/11","original_language":"en"},{"id":419786,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Who: Time Crash","video":false,"overview":"After Martha Jones parts company with the Doctor, his TARDIS collides with another, and he comes face to face with one of his previous incarnations.","genre_ids":[878,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.321,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/oXX7KUd8EQuJD0CQo8ofpU50Bn6.jpg","release_date":"2007-11-16","vote_average":7.705,"backdrop_path":"/boqvy9im9HTV3KfBWLio3oRl8qs.jpg","original_title":"Doctor Who: Time Crash","original_language":"en"},{"id":13351,"adult":false,"title":"Scooby-Doo! in Arabian Nights","video":false,"overview":"Scooby-Doo and Shaggy travel to Arabia to become the Caliph's Royal Food Tasters. But they bite off more than they can chew and are forced to run for their lives! It's a wild magic carpet ride as Scooby-Doo, Shaggy and their genie (Yogi Bear) and a jolly sailor named Sinbad (Magilla Gorilla) take you on an adventure of mistaken identities, exotic locations and fun-filled action and surprises!","genre_ids":[10751,14,16,10770,10402,9648,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7055,"vote_count":153,"poster_path":"/lCQ4e2iogfvLqWsfYLQedcOUgeh.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-03","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/1C6B8sGhhRWBmajZ4tQBSFbvmQy.jpg","original_title":"Scooby-Doo! in Arabian Nights","original_language":"en"},{"id":11579,"adult":false,"title":"Don Camillo's Last Round","video":false,"overview":"Bewildered, Don Camillo learns that Peppone intends to stand for parliament. Determined to thwart his ambitions, the good priest, ignoring the recommendations of the Lord, decides to campaign against him.","genre_ids":[35,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7253,"vote_count":184,"poster_path":"/tt2nV4pzFzFqBBGBpmfQIbdna4j.jpg","release_date":"1955-09-29","vote_average":7.236,"backdrop_path":"/iPXVSai8wqHVHJ5yRlzGtewVfRS.jpg","original_title":"Don Camillo e l'onorevole Peppone","original_language":"it"},{"id":12699,"adult":false,"title":"Hellraiser: Hellworld","video":false,"overview":"When five hardcore Internet gamers are invited to a special party thrown by the website Hellworld, they endure a night of unspeakable terror.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4369,"vote_count":376,"poster_path":"/p3QI77LO2TSeLfZ0CHdbw0uITef.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-06","vote_average":4.685,"backdrop_path":"/lXpBj7RDr7wShql0KpCLYHyYvdi.jpg","original_title":"Hellraiser: Hellworld","original_language":"en"},{"id":119321,"adult":false,"title":"Big Top Scooby-Doo!","video":false,"overview":"When Scooby and the gang hear of a werewolf plaguing a traveling circus, they go undercover as circus performers to get to the bottom.","genre_ids":[10751,16,35,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1159,"vote_count":211,"poster_path":"/i0zImtsknzWLl5OvAQ23Y3gfEYZ.jpg","release_date":"2012-10-09","vote_average":7.668,"backdrop_path":"/e4FPEArBE5sChp2ZGBgxP7UdsXL.jpg","original_title":"Big Top Scooby-Doo!","original_language":"en"},{"id":32916,"adult":false,"title":"Scooby-Doo! Abracadabra-Doo","video":false,"overview":"The gang goes on a trip to check on Velma's younger sister, Madelyn. She's been studying stage magic at the Whirlen Merlin Magic Academy, where apparently there have been sightings of a giant griffin. The gang decides to investigate.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,9648,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1169,"vote_count":262,"poster_path":"/hDfQ3DqU5fWKZinIGgo2psvLh4j.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-16","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/4m99oWQglMXNSLTrtXU6f9j9fGT.jpg","original_title":"Scooby-Doo! Abracadabra-Doo","original_language":"en"},{"id":823491,"adult":false,"title":"Out of Darkness","video":false,"overview":"In the Old Stone Age, a disparate gang of early humans band together in search of a new land. But when they suspect a malevolent, mystical, being is hunting them down, the clan are forced to confront a danger they never envisaged.","genre_ids":[12,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7734,"vote_count":120,"poster_path":"/9tG77VE7bP8ve79X86ABwHzDqbb.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-09","vote_average":5.696,"backdrop_path":"/hGDNYyED9uJVtROtp2K7ukF0jTz.jpg","original_title":"Out of Darkness","original_language":"en"},{"id":329505,"adult":false,"title":"Lola's Secret","video":false,"overview":"Young man has his dreams come true when the sexy new maid seduces him. But she also has a secret that leads to trouble.","genre_ids":[18,35,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1583,"vote_count":68,"poster_path":"/qaJ4iQngrLbyz9OgaQkJLppDN6m.jpg","r