 turns Daphne and Velma into Wrestle Maniacs. For a grand-slam finale the hockey mystery Diamonds Are A Ghoul's Best Friend introduces the chilling Frozen Fiend. When the gang dons sticks and pads, will they perform a hat trick...or get frozen stiff?","genre_ids":[10751,16,35,12,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2349,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/zAomc35eiVg7n72Nh0IZAf0FvKR.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-14","vote_average":9.9,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"What's New, Scooby-Doo? Vol. 5: Sports Spooktacular","original_language":"en"},{"id":70587,"adult":false,"title":"Spooky Buddies","video":false,"overview":"The nefarious Warwick the Warlock has returned from his astral imprisonment, and plans to make the final sacrifice for ultimate power - all he needs is the soul of a pure heart. The Buddies, alongside their new spectral friend Pip, race against the clock to defeat the sorcerer, who has enlisted the Halloween Hound to do his dirty work under the cover of the neighborhood festivities.","genre_ids":[35,10751,9648,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9548,"vote_count":162,"poster_path":"/cC6NleO3bn2FgFpkJx1RQvjccWL.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-20","vote_average":6.09,"backdrop_path":"/d79CoC9Hq3ZKuQr9v2SFMLtWiZV.jpg","original_title":"Spooky Buddies","original_language":"en"},{"id":65296,"adult":false,"title":"Humanité","video":false,"overview":"In a quiet little French town, two detectives are tasked with investigating the brutal rape and murder of a preteen girl.","genre_ids":[18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4899,"vote_count":110,"poster_path":"/fEEVsOpI21ZDY64tKMh4T3FZzCp.jpg","release_date":"1999-09-10","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/x2n7x2ZfMocYkzEY75g4UxvQYSC.jpg","original_title":"L'humanité","original_language":"fr"},{"id":298015,"adult":false,"title":"Night of the Living Doo","video":false,"overview":"In a spoof of 1972's The New Scooby-Doo Movies, Scooby-Doo and the Mystery Inc. gang pick up a hitchiking Gary Coleman. Soon after, the Mystery Machine proceeds to break down (multiple times) leaving them stranded at a haunted castle owned by David Cross.","genre_ids":[10751,16,35,12,9648,10770,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5167,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/aivTxgtMuUFbLPuGshi4OY4Nzla.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-31","vote_average":8.911,"backdrop_path":"/lDeequ9mKidTheyZqX1Q9KwhXY6.jpg","original_title":"Night of the Living Doo","original_language":"en"},{"id":14267,"adult":false,"title":"Female Trouble","video":false,"overview":"Dawn Davenport progresses from a teenage nightmare hell-bent on getting cha-cha heels for Christmas to a fame monster whose egomaniacal impulses land her in the electric chair.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7259,"vote_count":217,"poster_path":"/cqhIufhoORDMuFKEinV1IIYUBxD.jpg","release_date":"1974-10-11","vote_average":6.903,"backdrop_path":"/utsFSjBd6Ai56BwFB8s80S1a9bC.jpg","original_title":"Female Trouble","original_language":"en"},{"id":979660,"adult":false,"title":"Freaky Tales","video":false,"overview":"In 1987 Oakland, a mysterious force guides The Town's underdogs in four interconnected tales: teen punks defend their turf against Nazi skinheads, a rap duo battles for hip-hop immortality, a weary henchman gets a shot at redemption, and an NBA All-Star settles the score.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2023,"vote_count":208,"poster_path":"/lo5mfglsGeMYmAkSRXs9DATNJxk.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-04","vote_average":6.299,"backdrop_path":"/elZZLzhDzjRIIkGcIK0FGmZSUaq.jpg","original_title":"Freaky Tales","original_language":"en"},{"id":121828,"adult":false,"title":"Beyond Outrage","video":false,"overview":"As the police launch a full-scale crackdown on organized crime, it ignites a national yakuza struggle between the Sanno of the East and Hanabishi of the West. What started as an internal strife in Outrage has now become a nationwide war in Outrage Beyond.","genre_ids":[28,80],"medi